title: 2020 CFB Pick Em Week 9
description:
El Pres, Big Cat & Rico Bosco are back for another week of picks. After last week's reveal of the hype circle, Rico had a strong Saturday showing. However, Big Cat is the hottest in the crew and remains in the lead for Pat Hill Trophy!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
